{"items":[{"id":"31726","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>奇点定理：霍金发现的</p>\n<p>经过测算，黑洞中一定有一个体积无限小而密度无限大的奇点。听着很抽象是不是？可是奇点是确实存在的。</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1501488413,"created_at":1501488413,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"31676","user":{"id":"333185","nickname":"Treubler","avatar_url":"https://creation.codemao.cn//490/YW5kXzEwMDFfMzMzMTg1XzBfMTY5MTg5OTU0NTM5OV9EU3lLZUZZWg==.jpg","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>……</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1501480082,"created_at":1501480082,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"31624","user":{"id":"314171","nickname":"假编程猫258","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/d2ViXzEwMDFfMzE0MTcxXzMxNDE3MV8xNjU4Mzg4OTczNzc3XzMzMDRiYTk5.png","subject_id":211,"work_shop_name":"跃动工作室","work_shop_level":3,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>恭喜，你成功成为萌新院学生</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1501472127,"created_at":1501472127,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"31567","user":{"id":"194533","nickname":"成成4","avatar_url":"https://static-platform.codemao.cn/production/avatar/custom/98c02e00-76a4-4718-a87b-66f870e81387","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><dl>\n <dd>\n  黑洞\n  <span>（特殊天体）</span>\n </dd>\n</dl>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\">黑洞</a><span>是现代</span><a rel=\"nofollow\">广义相对论</a><span>中，宇宙空间内存在的一种</span><a rel=\"nofollow\">天体</a><span>。黑洞的引力很大，使得视界内的逃逸速度大于</span><a rel=\"nofollow\">光速</a><span>。</span></p>\n<p>1916年，德国天文学家<a rel=\"nofollow\">卡尔·史瓦西</a><span>（Karl Schwarzschild）通过计算得到了</span><a rel=\"nofollow\">爱因斯坦</a><a rel=\"nofollow\">引力场方程</a><span>的一个真空解，这个解表明，如果将大量物质集中于空间一点，其周围会产生奇异的现象，即在质点周围存在一个界面——“</span><a rel=\"nofollow\">视界</a><span>”一旦进入这个界面，即使光也无法逃脱。这种“不可思议的天体”被</span><a rel=\"nofollow\">美国</a><span>物理学家约翰·阿奇博尔德·惠勒（John Archibald Wheeler）命名为“黑洞”。</span></p>\n<p><b>“</b><a rel=\"nofollow\"><b>黑洞</b></a><b>是</b><a rel=\"nofollow\"><b>时空曲率</b></a><b>大到</b><a rel=\"nofollow\"><b>光</b></a><b>都无法从其事件视界逃脱的</b><a rel=\"nofollow\"><b>天体</b></a><b>”。</b><sup>[1-3]</sup><a rel=\"nofollow\">&nbsp;</a><span>黑洞无法直接观测，但可以借由间接方式得知其存在与质量，并且观测到它对其他事物的影响。借由物体被吸入之前的因高热而放出和γ</span><a rel=\"nofollow\">射线</a><span>的“边缘讯息”，可以获取黑洞存在的讯息。推测出黑洞的存在也可借由间接观测</span><a rel=\"nofollow\">恒星</a><span>或</span><a rel=\"nofollow\">星际云</a><span>气团绕行轨迹取得位置以及质量。</span></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\"></a><br></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/emoji/codemao/10.gif\"><br></p>\n<p><br></p></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1501414466,"created_at":1501414466,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"31553","user":{"id":"327139","nickname":"批小将","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FviuX3_jRke2XjiySPv-4KAsj6HM","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>4万首付，6万低价</p>\n<p>8万底价</p>\n<p>这么小的楼8万是不是要考虑一下呢</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1501412742,"created_at":1501412742,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"31550","user":{"id":"273719","nickname":"庄子休","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fjnw_wQNkSmshJhg8Q_hwIaZJTcS?attname=","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>欢迎你加入萌新院...</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1501410435,"created_at":1501410435,"earliest_comments":[]}],"offset":0,"limit":30,"total":6,"counted":true}